channel.title: A few facts you should know
channel.description:
K, I've noticed a lot of people posting shit like "o diz huw u mak a cumand!!111 it iz 4 leat pplz, n i no mor java koding dan u", This post is for you people..
Well, when you put a random method, maybe a case or two, then say you programmed.. You're wrong. Short and explanitory, if you think you're programming a private server because you know what a bracket is, I hope you go google a guide on java and read it.
Also, what I've noticed is that people are calling themselves "excellent coders", it's not called a coder.. It's called a programmer. There is "code", which is what you've put into your program (in this case, your private server). But for the love of god, don't misuse the word Code, Program, Programmer, or Programming. Because, honestly.. It makes you look like a retard. I know I've posted crap like that, when I was 8 years old. So, I honestly expect more from people who are over eight years old. If you have a third of a brain, you'll know that.
Next up, peoples Private Servers.. What happened to them? Recently I've seen people taking a Pimpscape, adding a command or two.. Actually, about three hundred commands, then adding a method, a few objects, and maybe a case if you have a brain, then saying you're an excellent "coder"? So many things wrong with that.. First of all, you're not programming OR making your private server better, all you're doing is adding commands to ruin the Private Server, adding a bit of lag, and then calling yourself an incorrect word. For the love of god, if you're going to make a Private Server, do it from scratch or use a decent base then atleast put some fucking effort into it..
There's a HUGE list of what I think should be fixed with this community, and if you have something to say about MSCP, post now. I will be glad to add it to the list and show the community their errors and what they need to fucking learn and fix.
Also, to the staff.. I honestly don't care what you think.. From what I've heard.. MSCP Is helpless, and I believe it is. But you don't need to fucking give up on us and go to MITB. You can atleast come here, tell the morons to stfu and go google a guide on Java then read it, instead of going away so you don't have to deal with our problems. You're the fucking staff, and you should do something about it.
^ Third time.
